  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The IOC Intergovernmental Coordination Group for the Pacific Tsunami Warning and Mitigation System (ICG/PTWS) and UNESCO Apia Office work together towards increased tsunami preparedness in SIDS MS and communities through in-country training on Tsunami Early Warning Systems, pilot Tsunami Ready recognition for communities and finalisation/updating of tsunami Standard Operating Proc&#xE9;dures (SOPs). Support is provided as well to the Pacific Island Countries and Territories Regional Working Group on Tsunami Warning and Mitigation System</narrative>
